      523.75,
      533.93,
      599.95
    ],
    "text": "South-West monsoon is gradually getting established over the island. Showers or thundershowers will occur at times in Western, Sabaragamuwa and North-western provinces and in Galle, Matara, Kandy and Nuwara-Eliya districts. Fairly heavy falls above 50 mm are likely at some places in the above areas.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      0.9599999785423279,
      9.960000038146973,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      603.37,
      533.86,
      640.75
    ],
    "text": "Several spells of showers will occur in Northern province and in Anuradhapura and Hambantota districts.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Iskoola Pota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      643.66,
      533.9,
      678.58
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers may occur at a few places in Uva province and in Ampara and Batticaloa district after 2.00 pm.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Iskoola Pota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      3.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      681.85,
      533.61,
      717.94
    ],
    "text": "Fairly strong winds about (30-40) kmph can be expected at times over Western slopes of the central hills, Northern, North-central, North-western and Southern provinces.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      3.9600000381469727,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      720.46,
      533.52,
      760.06
    ],
    "text": "The general public is kindly requested to take adequate precautions to minimize damage caused by temporary localized strong winds and lightning during thundershowers",
